\begin_layout Standard
We will start by reviewing IVPMs in the classical setting and then propose
 our quantum generalization.
 In the classical setting, there are several proposals for 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

imprecise probabilities
\begin_inset Quotes erd
